# Personality Classification System  
A Java/J2EE-based web application built using **JSP**, **Servlets**, **JDBC**, and **MySQL** that allows users to register, log in, upload datasets, and view personality classification results.

---

## ğŸš€ Project Overview  
The **Personality Classification System** is a web-based platform that classifies personality types based on uploaded datasets.  
The system enables:

- User Registration & Login  
- Uploading dataset files  
- Processing the dataset  
- Generating & viewing classification results  
- Searching datasets  
- Secure authentication using Java Servlets & Sessions  
- Database connectivity using JDBC & MySQL

This project demonstrates full-stack development using classic Java EE technologies.

